title: Laundry basket

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a laundry basket, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a front elevational view of a laundry basket showing my design;
FIG. 2 is a rear elevational view thereof;
FIG. 3 is a top plan view thereof;
FIG. 4 is a bottom plan view thereof;
FIG. 5 is a left side elevational view thereof;
FIG. 6 is a right side elevational view thereof;
FIG. 7 is a perspective view thereof;
FIG. 8 is a perspective view showing a cover portion of the laundry basket in its retracted position;
FIG. 9 is a perspective view showing the cover portion of the laundry basket in its extended position;
FIG. 10 is a perspective view showing the cover portion of the laundry basket in its closed position;
FIG. 11 is a front view showing the laundry basket in a slightly collapsed position; and,
FIG. 12 is a front view showing the laundry basket in a collapsed position.
